          "en": "My father (may God have mercy on him) narrated to us. He said: Sa'd ibn Abdullah narrated to us from Ayyub ibn Nuh from Muhammad ibn Abi Umayr from Bishr ibn Maslama from Misma' Abu Sayyar from Abu Abdillah al-Sadiq (peace be upon him), who said:",
